{
  "stem": "19218.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll go back here for a little bit to this Polish gentleman who helped us tremendously during-- during the rough times in the camps.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I indicated that he wanted to hide me in-- in-- We-- we hear stories, I mean, there-- there-- there were-- there were just enough Poles that wanted to do this.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And yet, this man knew what the end would be if-- if they ever would discover me in his place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they knew that the war was going badly for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a matter of-- of a few months before the liberation, and before the Russians were actually-- they occupied.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- they came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were the first to occupy our camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the camp also employed a lot of civilian people there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this is where Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Kolojejiik came in as one of the workers in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] to survive in camp, of course, we also had selections, which means Mengele came into the camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, Mengele was closer to me than you are.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was right there, looking you straight in your eyes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And of course, they looked at you to see whether you still had enough flesh on your bones.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Otherwise, you'd go to one side again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when he was done, I mean, they would always take away truckloads of people, because there were new arrivals coming in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were probably-- they could last longer than the ones which already worked to the bone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That's exactly the definition-- worked to the bone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was nothing but bones in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was a name for these people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They called them Muselmanns.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Muselmanns are usually thin people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- and this-- this is where they would take them away.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
